;; TEST-PURPOSE: Wisp expression field projection may project a layout field from a temporary expression.
;; TEST-ATOM: (make-pair 20 22).right lowers as expression projection and returns 22.
;; TEST-EXPECT: compile, run
;; TEST-COVERAGE: codegen.c:expression-level layout field projection
;; TEST-USES-ATOM: atom.codegen.category.80.wisp.codegen
;; TEST-MENU: branches/wisp-codegen/define-and-types/atom.codegen.80.wisp.codegen.define.and.types.rt.wisp.temp.field.projection
